# Local dev only. Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) and fill in ONE of the token
# options below. In production these are set as Worker secrets, not from this file.
#
# If you were issued a long-life access token, set this and leave the refresh token blank:
RTT_ACCESS_TOKEN=your-long-life-access-token
#
# If you were issued a refresh token instead, set this one (the Worker will mint
# short-life access tokens from it automatically) and leave RTT_ACCESS_TOKEN blank:
# RTT_REFRESH_TOKEN=your-refresh-token
#
# Optional: pin the API version (ISO date). Leave unset to always use the latest.
# RTT_API_VERSION=2026-04-09
